To make managing your health care even easier, we’re regularly adding new features.

In this release, you can take charge of your health with these enhancements:
• One touch searches for primary care doctors, urgent care centers and emergency rooms in the search section
• Additional categories in the records tab
• Ability to set weekly goals to stay motivated and improve your health
• Ability to re-enter the health survey to add or change answers.
